{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3008_00_01","textHome":"6岁那年，邻居的阿姨丢了钱包，我帮着一起@找的那件事清晰地印在了脑海中。从那之后，@我就以成为居委会的志愿者而努力……@回过神来，已经被称为了麻烦处理家，每天都@非常忙……但是我完全拒绝不了别人的请求。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":0}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3008_00_18","textHome":"我其实想做漫画家，画出自己理想中的恋爱！@咦？空手道也会继续哦？所以，目标就是成为@恋爱空手道漫画家！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":100}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3008_00_19","textHome":"太好了！创下了劈瓦新纪录！@力量在全身涌动！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.4,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.9,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":300800}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3008_00_20","textHome":"嗯……这样的话说不定能@进一步减少无用动作！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":300800}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3008_00_21","textHome":"看穿敌人的攻击做出极限的闪避！这样就能@让反击变得更快。不过，我还差的很远……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":300}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3008_00_22","textHome":"我逐渐能够靠对方微小的反应来预测出对方@接下来的动作了，只是全凭感觉。所以之后@我想要更加准确地做出预测！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":100}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3008_00_23","textHome":"我想通过空气的流动，来感知对方接下来的行动@与想法……！哎呀~，虽然我还没什么自信……@但是，我已经不再是从前的我了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"id":300800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":300800}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3008_00_24","textHome":"啊，你来的正好！我现在正缺人手！拜托了！@能帮帮我吗？这个就是我的委托！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":300800}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3008_00_25","textHome":"早上好！一天就从晨练开始吧！方便的话，@和我一起如何？早上做运动很舒服的哦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3008_00_26","textHome":"这份便当，其实是我自己做的~咦？不要露出@这么惊讶的表情啊~！我也是会做料理的嘛！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":200}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3008_00_27","textHome":"回家之后就是练习练习！宫本武藏说，@千日修以返初心，万日炼以达极致……@这便是修炼！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.6,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":200}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.1,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3008_00_03","textHome":"总之，没事就好……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.9,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300800}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3008_00_28","textHome":"这个敌人，还挺厉害嘛……咕！真是棘手啊……@这……道题目！完全解不开！@看不到要结束的征兆啊！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.4,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":300,"tear":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":200}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3008_00_29","textHome":"练习不止是身体上的动作，意念锻炼也很重要。@有时间的话，就在脑海中……哈啊！@……诶咿！……就这样！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3008_00_30","textHome":"一旦接受了委托就必须完成，不可以逃避。@所以这并不是什么轻松的事情……@但是，我不能视而不见！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":200}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3008_00_31","textHome":"真正的决斗如果不抱有觉悟来面对的话，是对@对手的不尊重。不留余地，竭尽全力去战斗吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3008_00_32","textHome":"这样的战斗最重要的是保持冷静！毕竟团战中@十分混乱……这是父亲告诉我的……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3008_00_33","textHome":"我最喜欢的招式就是上段回旋踢。踢击对手@上方。用这招取胜的时候，真是太爽了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":300800}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3008_00_34","textHome":"训练也有十分辛苦的时候。但如果逃避的话，@之后绝对会后悔的。所以，我要继续留在这里。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":300800,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3008_00_35","textHome":"我最喜欢的词就是「一击必杀」！很想尝试@一次，不过似乎做不到，对练空手道的人来说，@这就是理想吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":300800}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3008_00_36","textHome":"麻烦被解决之后的笑容真棒呢。心情一下子就@晴朗的感觉，让一旁看着的我也神清气爽了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":100}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3008_00_37","textHome":"成为魔法少女之后，我的身体素质也提高了，@对抗训练的时候要注意点力气。@这一点让人稍微有些不开心……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":300}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3008_00_04","textHome":"真是的！那家伙到底想要干什么！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":0}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3008_00_38","textHome":"突如其来的委托，虽然有着各种各样的难题，@但也能收获各种经验、学到各种东西，@将其吸收为自己的一部分。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":100}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3008_00_39","textHome":"一旦开始战斗，就要把精力集中在眼前的@对手，不能考虑多余的事情。脑海中只能@有一个念头，那就是胜利。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.4,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":200}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3008_00_40","textHome":"神滨真是个奇怪的地方，我经常能听到奇怪的@谣言。比如，嗯，什么来着……@啊，对了对了！开花少女之类的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3008_00_41","textHome":"我喜欢学校的制服。因为……这样就可以@正大光明地穿裙子了！这是学校的规定，@所以家人也插不了嘴啦——！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"id":300800,"motion":200}]},{"a